  61:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   *
  62:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   * The %Matrix class is the work-horse for all \em dense (\ref dense "note") matrices and vectors 
  63:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   * Vectors are matrices with one column, and row-vectors are matrices with one row.
  64:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   *
