  66:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   *
  67:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   * The first three template parameters are required:
  68:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   * \tparam Scalar_ Numeric type, e.g. float, double, int or std::complex<float>.
  69:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   *                 User defined scalar types are supported as well (see \ref user_defined_scalars 
  70:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   * \tparam Rows_ Number of rows, or \b Dynamic
  71:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/Matrix.h ****   * \tparam Cols_ Number of columns, or \b Dynamic
