  21:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * \brief Base class for all dense matrices, vectors, and expressions
  22:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   *
  23:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * This class is the base that is inherited by all matrix, vector, and related expression
  24:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * types. Most of the Eigen API is contained in this class, and its base classes. Other important
  25:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * classes for the Eigen API are Matrix, and VectorwiseOp.
  26:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   *
  27:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * Note that some methods are defined in other modules such as the \ref LU_Module LU module
  28:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * for all functions related to matrix inversions.
  29:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   *
  30:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * \tparam Derived is the derived type, e.g. a matrix type, or an expression, etc.
  31:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   *
  32:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * When writing a function taking Eigen objects as argument, if you want your function
  33:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * to take as argument any matrix, vector, or expression, just let it take a
  34:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * MatrixBase argument. As an example, here is a function printFirstRow which, given
  35:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * a matrix, vector, or expression \a x, prints the first row of \a x.
  36:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   *
  37:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * \code
  38:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****     template<typename Derived>
  39:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****     void printFirstRow(const Eigen::MatrixBase<Derived>& x)
  40:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****     {
  41:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****       cout << x.row(0) << endl;
  42:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****     }
  43:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * \endcode
  44:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   *
  45:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * This class can be extended with the help of the plugin mechanism described on the page
  46:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * \ref TopicCustomizing_Plugins by defining the preprocessor symbol \c EIGEN_MATRIXBASE_PLUGIN.
  47:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   *
  48:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/MatrixBase.h ****   * \sa \blank \ref TopicClassHierarchy
