 251:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/PlainObjectBase.h ****       * This method is intended for dynamic-size matrices, although it is legal to call it on any
 252:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/PlainObjectBase.h ****       * matrix as long as fixed dimensions are left unchanged. If you only want to change the numbe
 253:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/PlainObjectBase.h ****       * of rows and/or of columns, you can use resize(NoChange_t, Index), resize(Index, NoChange_t)
 254:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/eigen/Eigen/src/Core/PlainObjectBase.h ****       *
